All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
ChartDTO
The ChartDTO class is a data transfer object that encapsulates chart-related information.
DatabaseDTO
The DatabaseDTO class is a data transfer object that encapsulates database-related information.
FieldDTO
The FieldDTO class is a data transfer object that encapsulates field-related information.
KafkaTemplateSerializer
The KafkaTemplateSerializer class provides a mechanism for serializing and deserializing a KafkaTemplate object.
MetaModelDTO
The MetaModelDTO class is a data transfer object that encapsulates all the information needed for annotation processing.
MiniRealAnnotationProcessor
This class is an annotation processor that uses the DTOs and annotations.
ModelDTO
The ModelDTO class is a data transfer object that encapsulates model-related information.
ParamDTO
The ParamDTO class is a data transfer object that encapsulates parameter-related information.
SimAgent
The SimAgent annotation is used to mark types (classes or interfaces) that represent agents in a simulation model.
SimChart
The SimChart annotation is used to mark methods that generate or manipulate charts in a simulation model.
SimDB
The SimDB annotation is used to mark methods that are associated with a database table.
SimField
The SimField annotation is used to mark fields that are associated with a database table.
SimModel
The SimModel annotation is used to mark types (classes or interfaces) that are associated with a model.
SimParam
The SimParam annotation is used to mark parameters that are associated with a simulation model.
